'''羅伯特·葛蘭維爾·雷蒙'''（{{lang-en|Robert Granville Lemon}}，{{bd|1920年|9月22日|2000年|1月11日|}}），為美國職棒大聯盟的投手和總教練。他在1976年入選美國棒球名人堂。

雷蒙17歲時便加入了印地安人體系，並在1941年登上大聯盟。1943年至1945年間，雷蒙因為參與服役而缺席了3年職棒生涯。

1948年世界大賽，雷蒙拿下2勝，幫助印地安人拿下世界大賽冠軍。1954年，他更是以23勝7敗締造了印地安人隊史紀錄。

==早年==
雷蒙高中時就有在打棒球，並擔任球隊的游擊手。<ref name="Martin">{{cite news|url=https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=f3E_AAAAIBAJ&pg=7192,4228341&dq=bob+lemon+wilson+high+school&hl=en|title=My Favorite Big League Ball Player – Bob Lemon|date=1951-04-06|accessdate=2012-09-09|last=Martin|first=Johnny|newspaper=[[The_Mount_Airy_News|The Mount Airy News]]|page=13}}</ref>他在17歲時就和印地安人簽約，並開啟了他的職業生涯。<ref name="Minors">{{cite web|title=Bob Lemon Minor League Statistics & History|work=[[Baseball-Reference.com|Baseball-Reference.com]]|accessdate=2012-08-31|url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/minors/player.cgi?id=lemon-001rob|archive-date=2015-04-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150420222921/http://www.baseball-reference.com/minors/player.cgi?id=lemon-001rob|dead-url=no}}</ref>
==大聯盟生涯==
===多守位的工具人===
1941年9月9日，雷蒙登上大聯盟，不過他是以三壘手的身分出場。<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=1EQrAAAAIBAJ&pg=1534,5211259&dq=bob+lemon+200+wins&hl=en|title=Bob Lemon recounts glory years of Tribe|date=1978-06-11|accessdate=2012-09-01|newspaper=The Nevada Herald|page=8|last=Bradham|first=Kelly}}</ref>該年他出賽5場比賽，5個打數敲出1支安打。<ref>{{cite web|title=Bob Lemon 1941 Batting Gamelogs|work=[[Baseball-Reference.com|Baseball-Reference.com]]|accessdate=2012-09-07|url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/players/gl.cgi?id=lemonbo01&t=b&year=1941|archive-date=2016-08-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160810144356/http://www.baseball-reference.com/players/gl.cgi?id=lemonbo01&t=b&year=1941|dead-url=no}}</ref>當時他和另一名新秀捕手Jim Hegan同時升上大聯盟。<ref>{{cite book |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=62pwMklqJ2kC&pg=PA109&lpg=PA109&dq=bob+lemon+navy#v=onepage|title=Bill Veeck: Baseball's Greatest Maverick|year=2012|last=Dickson|first=Paul|publisher=Walker Publishing Company|location=New York|isbn=978-0-8027-1778-8}}</ref>{{rp|p.109}}不過到了1942年，雷蒙整年一支安打都打不出來。<ref name="Complete">{{cite web|url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/players/l/lemonbo01.shtml|work=[[Baseball-Reference.com|Baseball-Reference.com]]|accessdate=2012-09-09|title=Bob Lemon Statistics and History|archive-date=2021-05-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210530215220/https://www.baseball-reference.com/players/l/lemonbo01.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>1943年至1945年間，雷蒙和Hegan都去美軍服役而缺席了三個球季。<ref>{{cite news|url=https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=wAgeAAAAIBAJ&pg=5550,6278187&dq=bob+lemon+world+war&hl=en|title=Royals Manager Once A Flop As Major League Outfielder|date=1970-06-14|accessdate=2012-09-02|newspaper=[[The_Daily_News_(Kentucky)|Daily News]]|location=Bowling Green, Kentucky|page=17|last=Moore|first=Roger|agency=Associated Press}}</ref>他也在加入美軍前結婚。<ref name="Martin" /><ref name="Koppett">{{cite news|url=https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=kyMhAAAAIBAJ&pg=2439,5155480&dq=bob+lemon+1941+season&hl=en|title=Bob Lemon: No One Has A Bad Word About Him|date=1978-07-27|accessdate=2012-09-01|newspaper=[[Sarasota_Herald-Tribune|Sarasota Herald-Tribune]]|page=D|last=Koppett|first=Leonard|agency=New York Times News Service}}</ref>

1946年，雷蒙回到印地安人，並擔任中外野手。4月30日，陣中投手[[鮑伯·費勒|鮑伯·費勒]]投出無安打比賽。而費勒更是將他的無安打歸功於雷蒙優異的守備。<ref name="Feller">{{Cite book|url=https://archive.org/details/bobfellerslittle00bobf|quote=bob lemon.|pages=[https://archive.org/details/bobfellerslittle00bobf/page/40 40]|title=Bob Feller's Little Black Book of Baseball Wisdom|last1=Feller|first1=Bob|last2=Rocks|first2=Burton|isbn=0-8092-9843-0|year=2001|publisher=Contemporary Books|location=Chicago}}</ref>不過到了球季末，雷蒙開始改練投手。<ref name="Koppett" />當時雷蒙在服役期間就曾與老虎隊的Birdie Tebbetts和紅襪隊的[[約翰尼·佩斯基|約翰尼·佩斯基]]交手過，兩人也曾向當時印地安人的總教練[[盧·布德羅|盧·布德羅]]建議讓雷蒙改練投手。<ref name="Martin" /><ref name="Tips">{{cite news|url=https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=10gmAAAAIBAJ&pg=4461,4465903&dq=bob+lemon+1947&hl=en|title=Pitching Tips|agency=Associated Press|last=Lemon|first=Bob|date=1956-07-21|accessdate=2012-09-09|newspaper=[[The_Gettysburg_Times|The Gettysburg Times]]|page=5}}</ref>

為此，布德羅還曾向軍中同袍，同時也是洋基隊捕手的[[比爾·狄奇|比爾·狄奇]]詢問。而狄奇也非常樂見雷蒙擔任投手一事，<ref name="Boudreau">{{cite book|title=Lou Boudreau: Covering All the Bases|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=8eSUdoov0AEC&pg=PA86&lpg=PA86&dq=bob+lemon#v=onepage|year=1993|last1=Boudreau|first1=Lou|last2=Schneider|first2=Russell|isbn=0-915611-72-4|publisher=Sagamore Publishing|location=Chicago}}</ref>{{rp|p.86}}於是布德羅請投手教練[[梅爾·哈德|梅爾·哈德]]教導雷蒙投球。<ref name="Boudreau" />{{rp|p.93}}<ref>{{cite news|url=https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=fcxFAAAAIBAJ&pg=6794,1627262&dq=bob+lemon+1948+playoff+cleveland+indians+boston+red+sox&hl=en |title=Hall of Famer Boudreau Dies|page=B6|date=2001-08-12|accessdate=2012-09-01|newspaper=[[Portsmouth_Daily_Times|Portsmouth Daily Times]]|agency=Associated Press}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|newspaper=[[The_Milwaukee_Journal|The Milwaukee Journal]]|date=1948-10-08|page=2|title=Rival Deserves Assist on Lemon; Southworth Glad to Leave Home}}</ref><ref name="James">{{cite book|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=7FfRLE6I5EEC&pg=PA38&lpg=PA38&dq=bob+lemon#v=onepage|title=The Neyer/James Guide to Pitchers: An Historical Compendium of Pitching, Pitchers, and Pitches|last1=James|first1=Bill|last2=Neyer|first2=Rob|year=2004|publisher=Fireside|location=New York|isbn=0-7432-6158-5}}</ref>{{rp|p.38}}1946年，雷蒙雖然只拿下4勝5敗，不過防禦率只有2.49。隔年他出賽37場比賽，其中15場比賽擔任先發投手，整年拿下11勝5敗。<ref name="Tips" />而且他這年還有兩場比賽先發至少11局。<ref>{{cite web|title=Bob Lemon 1947 Pitching Gamelogs|work=[[Baseball-Reference.com|Baseball-Reference.com]]|accessdate=2012-09-09|url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/players/gl.cgi?id=lemonbo01&t=p&year=1947|archive-date=2016-08-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160811232329/http://www.baseball-reference.com/players/gl.cgi?id=lemonbo01&t=p&year=1947|dead-url=no}}</ref>

===全職投手與世界大賽===
1948年球季開打前，球隊主席Bill Veeck就給雷蒙加薪。<ref>{{cite news|url=https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=PgMkAAAAIBAJ&pg=3883,2855757&dq=bob+lemon+1948+season&hl=en|title=Bob Lemon Signs 1948 Tribe Contract|date=1948-01-01|accessdate=2012-09-01|page=12|agency=Associated Press|newspaper=[[Milwaukee_Journal_Sentinel|Milwaukee Sentinel]]}}</ref>他也成為球隊的二號先發。<ref name="Recognize">{{cite news|url=https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=SUVGAAAAIBAJ&pg=6471,4161089&dq=bob+lemon+1948+season&hl=en|page=B3|date=1998-06-20|accessdate=2012-09-01|newspaper=[[Portsmouth_Daily_Times|Portsmouth Daily Times]]|agency=Associated Press|title=Indians recognize team which won 1948 Series}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=W-RPAAAAIBAJ&pg=5059,6178320&dq=bob+lemon&hl=en|title=Bob Lemon Sweet Find For Indians|newspaper=[[Evening_Independent|The Evening Independent]]|location=St. Petersburg, Florida|date=1948-05-26|accessdate=2012-09-01|last=Reichler|first=Joe|page=14|agency=Associated Press}}</ref>6月30日，他投出了無安打比賽。那年他投出美聯最多的10場完封勝，<ref name="Complete" /><ref>{{cite news|url=https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=gxAvAAAAIBAJ&pg=3503,84173&dq=bob+lemon&hl=en|newspaper=[[The_Ottawa_Citizen|The Ottawa Citizen]]|title=Bob Lemon Hurls No-Hitter For Indians, Humbles Detroit Team To Record 11th Win|date=1948-07-01|accessdate=2012-08-31|agency=Associated Press}}</ref><ref name="Track">{{cite news|newspaper=[[The_Palm_Beach_Post|The Palm Beach Post]]|date=1978-07-25|accessdate=2012-08-31|title=Bob Lemon has a good track record|page=2C|url=https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=Vzw0AAAAIBAJ&pg=903,1580833&dq=bob+lemon&hl=en}}</ref>並拿下20勝14敗，成功獲選為美聯年度最佳投手。印地安人也以1場勝差打敗紅襪進入世界大賽。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/teams/CLE/1948-schedule-scores.shtml|title=1948 Cleveland Indians – Schedule, Box Scores and Splits|work=[[Baseball-Reference.com|Baseball-Reference.com]]|accessdate=2012-09-01|archive-date=2021-04-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210414202732/https://www.baseball-reference.com/teams/CLE/1948-schedule-scores.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/boxes/CLE/CLE194810010.shtml|title=October 1, 1948 Detroit Tigers at Cleveland Indians Play by Play and Box Score|work=[[Baseball-Reference.com|Baseball-Reference.com]]|accessdate=2012-09-01|archive-date=2020-08-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200819184241/https://www.baseball-reference.com/boxes/CLE/CLE194810010.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=Bob Lemon Hurls Today for Tribe; Yanks, Bosox Win|url=https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=r2EvAAAAIBAJ&pg=5944,117807&dq=bob+lemon&hl=en|newspaper=[[The_Modesto_Bee|The Modesto Bee]]|last=Rhoden|first=Ralph|agency=Associated Press|date=1948-10-01|accessdate=2012-09-01}}{{Dead link}}</ref>

印地安人讓[[鮑伯·費勒|鮑伯·費勒]]擔任第一戰先發，不過球隊以0比1落敗。而雷蒙在第二場比賽面對[[華倫·史潘|華倫·史潘]]以4比1奪勝。<ref name="Forty_eight">{{cite web|url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/pl/player_search.cgi?search=1948+world+series|title=1948 World Series – Cleveland Indians Over Boston Braves (4–2)|accessdate=2012-09-01|work=[[Baseball-Reference.com|Baseball-Reference.com]]|archive-date=2015-09-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150925003159/http://www.baseball-reference.com/pl/player_search.cgi?search=1948+world+series|dead-url=no}}</ref>費勒雖然在世界大賽吞下2敗，不過雷蒙在系列賽拿下2勝，防禦率僅1.65。<ref name="Forty_eight" />成功撐起印地安人投手輪值，也幫助球隊4勝2敗拿下世界大賽冠軍。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/boxes/BSN/BSN194810110.shtml|title=October 11, 1948 World Series Game 6, Indians at Braves|accessdate=2012-09-02|work=[[Baseball-Reference.com|Baseball-Reference.com]]|archive-date=2021-01-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210117201039/https://www.baseball-reference.com/boxes/BSN/BSN194810110.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>

而雷蒙的打擊能力也不容小覷，1949年8月，他曾締造打擊率2成95，並敲出6轟共11支長打。<ref>{{cite news|newspaper=[[Sunday_Herald_(Bridgeport,_Connecticut)|Sunday Herald]]|location=Bridgeport, Connecticut|page=36|url=https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=IGkmAAAAIBAJ&pg=6641,692209&dq=bob+lemon&hl=en|title=Bob Lemon Is Demon At Plate|last=Richman|first=Milton|date=1949-08-07|accessdate=2012-08-31|agency=United Press International}}</ref>1950年，雷蒙以單季23勝再次拿下美聯年度最佳投手殊榮。<ref>{{cite news|url=https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=VjwNAAAAIBAJ&pg=4957,432899&dq=bob+lemon&hl=en|title=Indians Clip Tigers Behind Lemon, 12 to 2|date=1950-09-30|agency=Associated Press|accessdate=2012-09-07|newspaper=[[Pittsburgh_Post-Gazette|Pittsburgh Post-Gazette]]|page=12}}</ref>1951年，當時雷蒙已經成為聯盟的最高薪選手。<ref>{{cite news|url=https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=FIpgAAAAIBAJ&pg=4837,6366573&dq=bob+lemon+1951+season&hl=en|title=Indians To Sign Lemon|date=1951-03-01|accessdate=2012-09-02|page=24|newspaper=[[Pittsburgh_Tribune-Review|Greensburg Daily Tribune]]|agency=United Press International}}</ref>該年他拿下17勝14敗，防禦率3.52。<ref name="Complete" />1952年，雷蒙拿下22勝11敗，防禦率2.50是生涯第二低。

1953年開幕戰，雷蒙面對白襪隊投出1安打完封勝。<ref>{{cite news|url=https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=QgUdAAAAIBAJ&pg=6131,568805&dq=bob+lemon+1952+season&hl=en|title=Lemon off to good start sixth 20-game season|last=Phlegar|first=Ben|agency=Associated Press|newspaper=[[Sarasota_Journal|Sarasota Journal]]|page=11|date=1954-05-06|accessdate=2012-09-02}}</ref>這年他投出21勝15敗，防禦率3.36。<ref name="Complete" />
===二闖世界大賽===
1954年，雷蒙以23勝7敗拿下美聯年度最佳投手，並順利帶領球隊闖進世界大賽。當年印地安人在例行賽只有154場比賽的賽程中拿下111勝，寫下了美聯紀錄。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/leagues/AL/|title=American League Team Win Totals|accessdate=2012-09-07|work=[[Baseball-Reference.com|Baseball-Reference.com]]|archive-date=2021-05-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210516010421/https://www.baseball-reference.com/leagues/AL/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Indians History Overview: The Glory Years|work=[[Mlb.com|Mlb.com]]|url=http://cleveland.indians.mlb.com/cle/history/cle_history_overview.jsp?story=3|accessdate=2012-09-07|archive-date=2016-08-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160820050823/http://cleveland.indians.mlb.com/cle/history/cle_history_overview.jsp?story=3|dead-url=no}}</ref>雷蒙在第一場比賽擔任先發，當時印地安人和巨人打完正規9局依舊維持2比2平手，然而雷蒙續投第10局時被Dusty Rhodes敲出再見3分砲輸球。<ref>{{cite news|url=https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=tVEgAAAAIBAJ&pg=6199,5376792&dq=bob+lemon&hl=en|title=Dejected Lopez Puts Faith in Bob Lemon For Fourth Game|date=1954-10-01|page=9|newspaper=[[The_Daytona_Beach_Morning_Journal|The Daytona Beach Morning Journal]]|agency=Associated Press}}</ref>在休息兩天後，總教練又讓雷蒙擔任第四場比賽的先發。不過由於休息天數過少，雷蒙無法以最佳狀態應戰，最後以4比7輸球。印地安人4連戰遭到橫掃出局，而雷蒙吞下2敗，防禦率高達6.75。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/players/l/lemonbo01-pitch.shtml|title=Bob Lemon Pitching Statistics & History|work=[[Baseball-Reference.com|Baseball-Reference.com]]|accessdate=2012-09-01|archive-date=2017-11-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171109124649/https://www.baseball-reference.com/players/l/lemonbo01-pitch.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>

1955年4月，雷蒙拿下5勝0敗。<ref>{{cite news|url=https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=0aNWAAAAIBAJ&pg=1214,7226330&dq=bob+lemon+1951+season&hl=en|title=Lemon Off To Brilliant Start For Cleveland Indians|last=Lundquist|first=Carl|date=1955-04-27|accessdate=2012-09-02|agency=United Press International|newspaper=[[Greensburg_Daily_Tribune|Greensburg Daily Tribune]]|page=23|archive-date=2021-11-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211126000528/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=0aNWAAAAIBAJ&pg=1214%2C7226330&dq=bob+lemon+1951+season&hl=en|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Bob Lemon 1955 Pitching Gamelogs|work=[[Baseball-Reference.com|Baseball-Reference.com]]|url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/players/gl.cgi?id=lemonbo01&t=p&year=1955|access-date=2020-10-04|archive-date=2016-08-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160810070016/http://www.baseball-reference.com/players/gl.cgi?id=lemonbo01&t=p&year=1955|dead-url=no}}</ref>那年他拿下美聯最多的18勝，<ref name="Complete" />其中更是連續5場比賽投出完投。1956年9月11日，雷蒙拿下生涯200勝。<ref>{{cite news|url=https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=A2hSAAAAIBAJ&pg=6755,4554212&dq=bob+lemon+wins+200th+game&hl=en|title=Lemon Wins 200th, Beats Orioles 3 to 1|date=1956-09-12|accessdate=2012-09-01|agency=Associated Press|page=11|newspaper=[[St._Petersburg_Times|St. Petersburg Times]]|archive-date=2021-11-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211117225936/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=A2hSAAAAIBAJ&pg=6755%2C4554212&dq=bob+lemon+wins+200th+game&hl=en|dead-url=no}}</ref>那年他拿下20勝14敗，也是他最後一個拿下單季20勝的球季。1957年8月13日，雷蒙因為手肘出現骨刺整季報銷。<ref>{{cite news|date=1957-08-14|accessdate=2012-09-02|agency=Associated Press|newspaper=[[The_Victoria_Advocate|The Victoria Advocate]]|title=Tribe's Lemon Out For Year|url=https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=ShZQAAAAIBAJ&pg=3454,4475454&dq=bob+lemon+bone+chips&hl=en}}</ref>該年他僅拿下6勝11敗，是繼1946年後勝率最低的一年。

1958年，雷蒙成為印地安人陣中年紀最大的球員。那年他出賽2場比賽就被送到3A，<ref>{{cite news|newspaper=[[Portsmouth_Daily_Times|The Portsmouth Times]]|title=Indians Send Bob Lemon To San Diego|date=1958-04-25|accessdate=2012-09-01|page=21|url=https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=VMpQAAAAIBAJ&pg=3647,5474793&dq=bob+lemon+san+diego&hl=en|agency=Associated Press}}</ref>後來他在5月25日回到大聯盟。該年他出賽9場比賽，吞下1敗。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/players/gl.cgi?id=lemonbo01&t=p&year=1958|title=Bob Lemon 1958 Pitching Gamelogs|work=[[Baseball-Reference.com|Baseball-Reference.com]]|accessdate=2012-09-02|archive-date=2016-08-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160811102147/http://www.baseball-reference.com/players/gl.cgi?id=lemonbo01&t=p&year=1958|dead-url=no}}</ref>總計他生涯一共拿下207勝128敗，後來球隊在7月將他放進讓渡名單內。<ref>{{cite news|url=https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=8DogAAAAIBAJ&pg=4292,355228&dq=bob+lemon+1956+season&hl=en|date=1958-07-03|accessdate=2012-09-02|page=14|title=Cleveland Indians Ask For Waivers On Bob Lemon|agency=Associated Press|newspaper=[[Sarasota_Herald-Tribune|Sarasota Herald-Tribune]]}}</ref>
===退休===
1959年，雷蒙來到印地安人的春訓基地，並告知總教練[[喬·高登|喬·高登]]他想從後援投手出發。不過他在3月5日因自認無法跟上年輕人的腳步而宣布退休。<ref>{{cite news|url=https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=k-xkAAAAIBAJ&pg=3834,851941&dq=bob+lemon&hl=en|title=Bob Lemon Announces Retirement: Young Fellows Just Too Fast|date=1959-03-06|accessdate=2012-08-31|newspaper=[[Edmonton_Journal|The Edmonton Journal]]|page=8|agency=Associated Press|archive-date=2021-11-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211124143633/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=k-xkAAAAIBAJ&pg=3834%2C851941&dq=bob+lemon&hl=en|dead-url=no}}</ref>於是他轉任球隊的球探。

雷蒙生涯拿下207勝，另外還敲出274支安打，生涯擊出37轟為美聯投手史上第二高。<ref name="Gallagher">{{cite book|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=xEohYBGQfEgC&pg=PA295&lpg=PA295&dq=bob+lemon#v=onepage|accessdate=2012-09-07|year=2003|title=The Yankees Encyclopedia|edition=Sixth|last=Gallagher|first=Mark|publisher=Sports Publishing|location=Champaign, Illinois|isbn=1-58261-683-3|editor=Susan M. McKinney}}</ref>{{rp|p.198}}1998年6月20日，球隊將雷蒙的21號球衣退休。這也使得當時身穿21號的總教練Mike Hargrove換成背號30號。而雷蒙也是印地安人隊史第6位獲得此殊榮的球員。<ref name="Recognize" />

1976年1月22日，雷蒙成功入選名人堂。<ref>{{cite news|url=https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=xxMyAAAAIBAJ&pg=1219,1772780&dq=bob+lemon&hl=en|newspaper=[[The_Gazette_(Montreal)|The Gazette]]|date=1976-01-23|accessdate=2012-08-31|title=Fame renews ink of premier pitchers Lemon and Roberts|page=21|agency=Associated Press}}</ref>雷蒙在球員生涯有著一顆非常具宰制力的滑球，這也是為何他能入選名人堂的主要原因。<ref name="James" />{{rp|p.38}}{{rp|p.278}}
